"order, and you leave the room."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2508
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_Mb_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You find Mal doing a tour of the ship. He says he's looking for some hidden "
"areas designed by the ship's engineers. Strange, what's he talking about?"

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2511
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_Mb_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find Mal doing a tour of the ship. Together, you enter the cockpit. It's"
" empty, and the ship is on autopilot. Where did the pilot go? Mal sits in "
"the pilot's chair and stares into the blackness of space. Suddenly, he "
"realizes he was in this sector a few years ago. Mal opens the navigation "
"panel and enters all the beacons he can remember into the navigator."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2544
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_W_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You enter the cockpit. Wash is playing with little toy dinosaurs, mimicking "
"a bloody battle. He growls and snorts while clashing the toy creatures "
"together. Bewildered, you silently exit the cockpit, leaving the pilot and "
"trying to forget what you saw."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2545
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_W_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You find the pilot in the cargo hold, temporarily converted into a gym. Wash"
" is playing ball with other crew members. Seeing you and your questioning "
"look, Wash drops the ball and says with surprise, \"Oh gods, the spaceship "
"is flying at huge speed through space. Anything could happen! Who's flying "
"this thing?\" After a minute, Wash rushes to the cockpit."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2548
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_W_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter the cockpit and find Wash lying on the floor. He's tinkering with "
"the ship's control mechanism. A couple of minutes later, he reports that "
"he's fixed some equipment defects, and the ship has become more "
"maneuverable."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2587
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_Z_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find Zoe in the mess hall. She's peeling an apple with a combat knife. "
"You sit down next to her, take out your own knife, and take an apple too. As"
" you talk, you remember the old front-line days. Not noticing how time flew,"
" you stand up from the table and head to your quarters."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2590
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_Z_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter the cargo bay. Zoe is tinkering with the newly \"acquired\" cargo "
"crates, arranging them against the walls. After a while, she kicks one of "
"the crates into the center. Zoe explains that among the junk, there's "
"something valuable."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2627
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_I_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter Inara's shuttle uninvited, discovering the airlock wasn't locked. "
"Inara is setting tea things on the table. She's clearly in a good mood and "
"invites you to sit. You start a conversation over a cup of tea. The next "
"thing you see is the ceiling of your quarters. Oh, those Companion tricks. "
"Next time, you should knock."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2630
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_I_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You knock on the airlock of Inara's shuttle. Getting permission to enter, "
"you tell Inara about the current status of your mission. Inara asks you to "
"leave her shuttle, but adds at the last moment that she has a client in this"
" sector, and he has made a prepayment."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2663
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_J_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find Jayne in the mess hall. He has laid out a pile of parts from "
"different guns all over the dining table and is polishing each one to a "
"shine. You decide not to distract him from this \"important\" task."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2666
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_J_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You meet Jayne in the corridor. He says he kept something from the last raid"
" in his stash. The client refused to pay for the goods, so now it's ours. "
"Jayne points to a weapon hidden in one of the lockers."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2699
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_K_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter Kaylee's quarters after knocking and waiting for a \"Come in!\" "
"response. Kaylee is acting childish, making faces and dancing in front of "
"the mirror, dressed in a fluffy pink dress. You watch for a bit and then "
"leave."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2702
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_K_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"When you enter the engine room, Kaylee, covered in soot and holding a "
"wrench, greets you happily. She informs you that because of your cutting "
"corners on buying important ship parts, she secretly worked on the engine, "
"and now it's much more efficient."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2753
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_S_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter the infirmary. Simon is conducting his usual inventory of medical "
"supplies. Noticing your wound after a recent skirmish, he invites you to sit"
" on the couch and puts on his gloves. After cleaning the wound and a few "
"stitches, he informs you that you'll be fine. You thank the doctor and head "
"to your quarters."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2756
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_S_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You enter the infirmary. Simon is working at the medical terminal. Seeing "
"you enter, he quickly stands up and goes for a medical gown, saying he'll "
"patch you up, while taking off his vest. You refuse medical help, explaining"
" that your wound after the last skirmish isn't significant. Simon "
"reluctantly puts down the gown and tools. Sitting back down at the terminal,"
" he reports that he managed to order modern medical equipment through his "
"channels."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2790
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_R_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find River in the infirmary. Hugging her knees, she rocks back and forth"
" and keeps repeating the same words: \"Two by two, hands of blue.\" You "
"leave her alone."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2793
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_R_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You search for River all over the ship, but she's nowhere to be found. Seems"
" like she's hiding again. After a long search, you hear her voice from "
"somewhere behind the internal hull plating. After convincing her to come out"
" from the maintenance tunnels, you discover she has a memory card in her "
"hands. After analyzing the data, you find the coordinates of a smuggler's "
"stash and enter them into the navigator."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2796
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"RIVER_CACHE\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You arrive at the coordinates. It's a tiny rock with almost zero gravity. "
"After scanning the asteroid, you find an entrance to a small bunker under "
"the surface. Someone has hidden their loot inside."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2831
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_D_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You find the priest in his cabin. He's rereading the Bible again. You decide"
" not to distract him and leave."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2832
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_D_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
"You find the priest in his cabin. He is reciting a prayer aloud. You decide "
"not to distract him and leave."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2835
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_D_GOOD_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You find the priest in the cockpit. He suggests using his old contacts to "
"escape the pursuit. Without thinking twice, you agree. The pastor calls a "
"nearby Federation cruiser over the intercom and gives it some instructions."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2840
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[1]"
msgstr ""
"You are going to talk to a person, but he decided to take a nap while the "
"drive is charged.You don't want to wake him up."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2841
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[2]"
msgstr ""
