"fact that he has a lunch."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2846
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"You have enthusiastically discussing recent events with a person until a "
"signal of a charged FTL drive is heard."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2847
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[7]"
msgstr ""
"You go to talk to a person, but he smokes some incredibly smelly "
