#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2850
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[10]"
msgstr ""
"You find a person who plays on a glib of a melody from advertising.After "
"listening a little, you come back."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2852
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[11]"
msgstr ""
"The person says that on the previous ship he was a cleaner.He is satisfied "
"with the current work, and he copes with everything."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:2853
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"NOTHING2_HUMAN_TEXT\"]/text[12]"
msgstr ""
"You go to talk to a person, but find him behind cleaning the keyboard on the"
