msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//eventList[@name=\"PLANET_ENGE_ONE_MISSLE\"]/event[2]/text"
msgstr ""
"You lay a missile projectile under one of the doors.An explosion is heard, "
"and a bunch of dust rises into the air.When it dissipates, you see that the "
"steel door was knocked out by an explosion, it is lying near the entrance to"
" the spacious room.Your crew goes inside.Most of all, it looks like a "
"laboratory or some assembly workshop.Unknown mechanisms are everywhere, "
"everything is covered with a large layer of dust and most likely does not "
"work.Your attention is attracted by one device that is still in working "
"condition.The instructions say that it allows you to improve any missile gun"
" installed on the ship, so that it will not need ammunition!It looks very "
"attractive."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:11973
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"PLANET_ENGE_UPGRADE_TEXT\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"You set your tool in the mechanism.He begins to carry out the necessary "
"adjustments ..."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:11976
msgid ""
"data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"PLANET_ENGE_UPGRADE_TEXT_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"... and finally improves your gun.Now ammunition will not end when shooting "
"from it!You are still a step closer to the fulfillment of your mission, and "
"now it's time to prepare for a jump."

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:11980
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//event[@name=\"PLANET_ENGE_UPGRADE_2\"]/text"
