#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:64988
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT1_FM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a small trade station. The owner contacts you: "
"\"Hello, my name is Henry Quan. I've been trading here recently. You can buy"
" something from me or even donate unwanted resources for the station's "
"development...\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:64991
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT2_FM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a small trade station. The owner contacts you: "
"\"Hi there, I'm Bethany Jones, just Bethany is fine. I bought this station "
"recently and now I trade all sorts of things here. Buy something! Or even "
"better, gift me resources for the development of my little station...\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:64994
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT3_FM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a small trade station. The station owner contacts "
"you: \"Good day, old Adam is ready for trade operations. Donations for the "
"development of my humble trading post are also welcome...\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:64997
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT4_FM\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a small trade station. The owner contacts you: "
"\"Hello, friend! I am the trader Abe Isamu. Take a look at my goods. Besides"
" that, I could expand my inventory if you donate something for the "
"development of this little station...\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:65000
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a familiar trade station. Henry contacts you: "
"\"Hello again! Buy something or donate your scrap - everything will be "
"useful for the station's development...\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:65003
