msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a familiar trade station. Bethany contacts you: "
"\"Hi there, handsome! I've updated my stock, check it out! Hmm, where is "
"that promised gift for my super-station?..\""

#: src-ru/data/events.xml.rawclobber:65006
msgid "data/events.xml.rawclobber$//textList[@name=\"META_TRADER_TEXT3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"Near the beacon, you find a familiar trade station. The owner reports: "
"\"Good day, old Adam is glad to see you again. And I am still accepting "
"donations to expand the business...\""

